OL,7,FThe Post Office should not have been
OL,8,Finvolved in administering compensation
OL,9,Fschemes for sub-postmasters wrongly
OL,10,Fconvicted as a result of the Horizon
OL,11,FIT scandal, the organisation's chief
OL,12,Fexecutive has said.
OL,14,FNick Read made the remarks as part of
OL,15,Fevidence he gave to the Post Office
OL,16,FHorizon IT Inquiry on Thursday, the
OL,17,Fsecond of three days in which he is
OL,18,Fbeing questioned.
