OL,7,FMr Read - who will step down as chief
OL,8,Fexecutive next year - said the Post
OL,9,FOffice's involvement in the process
OL,10,F"was always going to be difficult"
OL,11,Fgiven the "level of trust and
OL,12,Fconfidence that many of the victims
OL,13,Fwill have in the Post Office".
OL,15,FHe had earlier told the inquiry he
OL,16,Ffelt it was "astonishing" the Post
OL,17,FOffice itself was involved in paying
OL,18,Fcompensation.
