OL,7,FMr Read also said he is "unaware" of
OL,8,Fwhat progress has been made as part of
OL,9,Fwork to assure current Horizon data is
OL,10,Freliable.
OL,12,FThe inquiry's lead counsel, Jason Beer
OL,13,FKC, asked Mr Read if "further work on
OL,14,FHorizon assurance and Horizon data
OL,15,Fassurance been undertaken to your
OL,16,Fknowledge?".
OL,18,FMr Read responded: "Not to my
OL,19,Fknowledge - I am unaware as to what
OL,20,Fprogress has been made over July,
OL,21,FAugust and September."
