OL,7,FHe said in a witness statement
OL,8,Fdiscussed at the inquiry: "Private
OL,9,Fprosecutions were presented to me as a
OL,10,Fhistoric issue that had ceased before
OL,11,F2015 and that I did not need to dig
OL,12,Finto the details of what had happened
OL,13,Fat Post Office in the past as this
OL,14,Fconduct had ended."
OL,16,FMr Read also admitted he was not made
OL,17,Faware of the "scale and enormity" of
OL,18,Fthe Horizon IT scandal before taking
OL,19,Fthe top job.
