OL,7,FBetween 1999 and 2015, over 700 Post
OL,8,FOffice sub-postmasters were convicted
OL,9,Fof theft or false accounting and
OL,10,Fthousands more were forced to make up
OL,11,Fshortfalls due to a problem with
OL,12,FFujitsu's Horizon software.
OL,14,FFour suicides were blamed on the
OL,15,Fscandal.
