OL,7,FWho is Nick Read?
OL,9,FNick Read replaced Paula Vennells as
OL,10,FPost Office chief executive in 2019,
OL,11,Famid mounting criticism of her
OL,12,Fhandling of the Horizon IT scandal.
OL,14,FHe had previously headed up Nisa
OL,15,FRetail and the now-defunct energy
OL,16,Fsupplier Extra Energy, and, upon
OL,17,Fjoining the Post Office, was set the
OL,18,Fremit to "right the wrongs of the
OL,19,Fpast".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
