OL,7,FMr Read has said he wants to use his
OL,8,Fappearance at the inquiry to prove
OL,9,Fthat "nothing like this can ever
OL,10,Fhappen again".
OL,12,FBut the incumbent head of the Post
OL,13,FOffice has faced scrutiny over
OL,14,Fallegations of bullying in the years
OL,15,Fthat have followed Sir Alan Bates
OL,16,Fleading sub-postmasters to a High
OL,17,FCourt victory over the organisation in
OL,18,F2019.
